        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">We will now go back to the earlier example of classifying 100 people (which includes 40 pregnant women and the remaining 60 are not pregnant women and men with a fat belly) as pregnant or not pregnant. Out of 40 pregnant women 30 pregnant women are classified correctly and the remaining 10 pregnant women are classified as not pregnant by the machine learning algorithm. On the other hand, out of 60 people in the not pregnant category, 55 are classified as not pregnant and the remaining 5 are classified as pregnant.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
