    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><h4 class="mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-7">What does precision mean?</h4></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><strong>Precision</strong> should ideally be 1 (high) for a good classifier. <strong>Precision</strong> becomes 1 only when the numerator and denominator are equal i.e <strong>TP = TP +FP</strong>, this also means <strong>FP</strong> is zero. As <strong>FP</strong> increases the value of denominator becomes greater than the numerator and <strong>precision</strong> value decreases (which we don’t want).</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">So in the pregnancy example, <strong>precision</strong> = 30/(30+ 5) = 0.857</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Now we will introduce another important metric called <strong>recall</strong>. <strong>Recall</strong> is also known as <strong>sensitivity </strong>or <strong>true positive rate</strong> and is defined as follows:</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
